You need to be responsible, too. Understand?

27
00:01:56,330 --> 00:01:57,930
Lin Xichi!

28
00:01:58,610 --> 00:02:00,210
Lin Xichi!

29
00:02:00,930 --> 00:02:04,269
Lin Xichi! Don't get upset.

30
00:02:04,269 --> 00:02:06,689
She is straightforward, please don't take it seriously.

31
00:02:06,689 --> 00:02:08,610
She's right!

32
