I thought I was here to play with animals.

33
00:02:12,668 --> 00:02:17,209
I never thought I would need to do these things.

34
00:02:17,209 --> 00:02:19,910
I actually feel disgusted.

35
00:02:19,910 --> 00:02:23,149
I'm not sure if I truly like this job.

36
00:02:23,149 --> 00:02:25,570
I... I understand.

37
00:02:25,570 --> 00:02:28,528
When I first came here, I started with cleaning cages, too.

38
00:02:28,529 --> 00:02:30,070
I felt disgusted, too.

39
00:02:30,070 --> 00:02:32,708
But think about it! Once you become a vet,

40
00:02:32,708 --> 00:02:36,788
you'll have to deal with many dirtier and harder things.

41
00:02:36,788 --> 00:02:41,010
I guess that's the difference between a profession and an interest.

42
00:02:42,630 --> 00:02:44,589
I'm sorry, Senior Ye!

43
00:02:44,589 --> 00:02:48,170
I don't think I'm ready to enter this profession yet.

44
00:03:16,489 --> 00:03:17,989
Chi-chi.

45
00:03:29,550 --> 00:03:31,460
Chi-chi,

46
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,350
what's wrong?

47
00:03:37,029 --> 00:03:41,250
Can I go to the archery practice with you together tomorrow?

48
00:03:42,129 --> 00:03:44,650
What about the pet shop?

49
00:03:47,789 --> 00:03:51,729
I'm glad you asked to go with me.

50
00:03:51,729 --> 00:03:56,529
But you were so excited to go to the pet shop back then.

51
00:03:56,529 --> 00:04:01,169
Right now, you... what happened?

52
00:04:06,190 --> 00:04:08,789
I'll wait for you there tomorrow.

53
00:04:12,389 --> 00:04:14,530
Have some milk!

54
00:04:14,530 --> 00:04:17,369
My laundry is done, I'll go get it.

55
00:05:02,007 --> 00:05:06,407
[All Things Bright and Beautiful]

56
00:05:06,407 --> 00:05:09,008
But think about it! Once you become a vet,

57
00:05:09,008 --> 00:05:12,408
you'll have to deal with many dirtier and harder things.

58
00:05:12,408 --> 00:05:16,709
I guess that's the difference between a profession and an interest.

59
00:05:47,529 --> 00:05:49,430
Have you eaten yet?

60
00:05:52,249 --> 00:05:53,949
I don't feel like eating.

61
00:05:56,170 --> 00:05:58,109
What happened?

62
00:06:05,269 --> 00:06:07,169
Someone bullied you?

63
00:06:09,489 --> 00:06:11,309
It's not a big deal.

64
00:06:11,309 --> 00:06:13,909
It's just that I feel incompetent.

65
00:06:13,909 --> 00:06:17,050
I'm always late to the pet shop and dropping things.

66
00:06:17,050 --> 00:06:19,550
I'm so clumsy.

67
00:06:19,550 --> 00:06:22,570
I feel like I'm always others' burden.

68
00:06:23,269 --> 00:06:26,609
Lin Xichi, you lost the arm wrestling,

69
00:06:26,609 --> 00:06:28,930
but you insisted on working at the pet shop.

70
00:06:28,930 --> 00:06:32,030
Do you have any idea how pissed off I was?

71
00:06:32,030 --> 00:06:37,089
That was the first time you broke our game rule and ran away.

72
00:06:37,089 --> 00:06:40,169
Now you're quitting just because you're not happy?

73
00:06:40,169 --> 00:06:43,910
You're going to break your promise for those petty things?

74
00:06:46,470 --> 00:06:48,230
I'm sorry!

75
00:06:48,970 --> 00:06:50,949
Don't apologize to me!

76
00:06:50,949 --> 00:06:53,409
You're responsible for your choice.

77
00:06:53,409 --> 00:06:55,790
Don't do something you might regret.

78
00:06:56,989 --> 00:07:00,529
Since you've made up your mind, you should stick to it.

79
00:07:00,529 --> 00:07:02,589
Don't make me look down on you.

80
00:07:09,409 --> 00:07:11,570
Look at yourself!

81
00:07:15,769 --> 00:07:18,329
Come! Let's have some noodles.

82
00:07:20,230 --> 00:07:21,970
With an egg!

83
00:07:22,870 --> 00:07:27,570
[Pupurazzi]

84
00:08:08,309 --> 00:08:09,809
Chi-chi.

85
00:08:13,030 --> 00:08:15,269
I'm here to look around.

86
00:08:15,269 --> 00:08:16,930
I need to go now.

87
00:08:16,930 --> 00:08:21,049
The manager and Yi Fang are having their days off.

88
00:08:21,049 --> 00:08:25,570
They've fallen sick but I can't manage the shop all by myself.

89
00:08:40,030 --> 00:08:43,629
Poor little things! No one's taking care of them.

90
00:08:43,629 --> 00:08:46,029
Should I call the manager?

91
00:08:46,029 --> 00:08:48,369
No, let her take a good rest at home.

92
00:08:48,370 --> 00:08:50,529
Don't make her worried!

93
00:08:51,429 --> 00:08:54,608
The manager has been taking care of them and I secretly learned how to do it.

94
00:08:54,608 --> 00:08:56,390
Leave it to me!

95
00:09:03,050 --> 00:09:06,550
Here's your food. Dig in!

96
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:10,269
Qi Qi, eat slowly.

97
00:09:16,710 --> 00:09:18,310
Here!

98
00:09:20,490 --> 00:09:22,210
Slowly.

99
00:09:23,950 --> 00:09:28,448
You're so good at it, looks like you'll soon be doing things other than cleaning cages.

100
00:09:28,448 --> 00:09:30,049
Really?

101
00:09:31,830 --> 00:09:33,448
Should we start today?

102
00:09:33,448 --> 00:09:35,329
Let's trim the dogs' claws.

103
00:09:35,329 --> 00:09:38,869
I was the one trimming my dog's claws when I'm home.

104
00:09:38,869 --> 00:09:41,069
But be careful, don't cut their quicks.

105
00:09:41,069 --> 00:09:43,950
No problem, all I need is an opportunity.

106
00:09:45,490 --> 00:09:48,208
Xiang Xiang, we're going to trim your claws.

107
00:09:48,209 --> 00:09:51,070
It doesn't know you well, so I'll hold it for you.

108
00:09:51,070 --> 00:09:52,630
Sure.

109
00:10:06,649 --> 00:10:11,009
Don't worry! I won't cut your quicks.

110
00:10:39,749 --> 00:10:41,789
Watch out! Watch out!

111
00:10:43,329 --> 00:10:45,769
- He bit you.
- I'm fine.

112
00:10:45,769 --> 00:10:48,948
Don't chase after it! Take your stuff, let's go to the epidemic prevention station.
- It's okay.

113
00:10:48,948 --> 00:10:50,930
We must go.

114
00:10:52,889 --> 00:10:55,789
- Fine.
- Let's go!

115
00:10:58,569 --> 00:11:02,109
Have you been to the pet shop today? Is everything going smoothly?

116
00:11:06,429 --> 00:11:08,448
I'm going to the epidemic prevention station, I'll talk to you later.

117
00:11:08,448 --> 00:11:10,510
Epidemic prevention station?

118
00:11:10,510 --> 00:11:13,609
- Let's go!
- Hello? Hello?

119
00:11:14,390 --> 00:11:16,390
What an idiot!

120
00:11:17,730 --> 00:11:20,409
Tell the coach I have something pressing and need the day off.

121
00:11:37,730 --> 00:11:39,330
Press it.

122
00:11:39,330 --> 00:11:41,309
Why are you here?

123
00:11:42,810 --> 00:11:46,569
What's wrong with you? Why didn't you look after her?

124
00:11:46,569 --> 00:11:50,669
And you! You're working at the pet shop, you should protect yourself.

125
00:11:50,669 --> 00:11:55,300
- Why were you being so careless?
- That's none of your business! And I was dealing with dogs and cats.

126
00:11:55,309 --> 00:11:58,249
It's inevitable! Aren't you here out of concern?

127
00:11:58,249 --> 00:12:00,190
Why are you questioning me?

128
00:12:02,070 --> 00:12:04,170
If this happens again,

129
00:12:04,170 --> 00:12:07,650
I'll teach the dog owner a good lesson.

130
00:12:10,089 --> 00:12:13,849
- I'll take you back to school.
- I want to go back to the pet shop.

131
00:12:13,849 --> 00:12:15,730
- No way!
- No way!

132
00:12:20,469 --> 00:12:22,229
Both of you are rarely on the same page.

133
00:12:22,229 --> 00:12:24,169
Keep your arm dry for today.

134
00:12:24,170 --> 00:12:27,928
And these are the dates for the four injections, get them on time!

135
00:12:27,928 --> 00:12:29,900
Let me take it!

136
00:12:36,730 --> 00:12:38,670
I thought you wouldn't come today.

137
00:12:38,670 --> 00:12:41,929
Yeah! Initially, I didn't plan to come to the shop.

138
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:46,500
But I've read the book you gave me, "All Things Bright and Beautiful.

139
00:12:46,528 --> 00:12:48,108
I couldn't help thinking...

140
00:12:48,108 --> 00:12:52,549
I must become an interesting and caring vet.

141
00:12:52,549 --> 00:12:55,769
Then, before I knew it, I was already in front of the shop.

142
00:12:55,769 --> 00:13:00,069
I wish that animals would find it lucky to have me as their vet.

143
00:13:03,250 --> 00:13:08,009
But did I gift you that book?

144
00:13:09,810 --> 00:13:12,209
You have a copy, too.

145
00:13:14,690 --> 00:13:17,649
Yeah, it's a good book.

146
00:13:19,170 --> 00:13:22,569
A handsome guy sent it here.

147
00:13:24,070 --> 00:13:25,970
I have a copy, too.

148
00:13:29,109 --> 00:13:31,009
I see.

149
00:13:31,769 --> 00:13:36,229
Yes, luckily, I came today! I got to take care of Xiang Xiang and Qi Qi.

150
00:13:36,229 --> 00:13:39,500
I got a minor injury, but it was worth it.

151
00:13:39,549 --> 00:13:41,849
You're an animal lover,

152
00:13:41,850 --> 00:13:44,750
I'm sure you're ready to be a vet.

153
00:13:45,989 --> 00:13:51,169
Tomorrow, the day after tomorrow, the days after that, I'll wait for you at the shop.

154
00:13:52,250 --> 00:13:53,850
Lin Xichi!

155
00:13:57,070 --> 00:14:00,089
I've got you those other medicines. Let's go now!

156
00:14:01,209 --> 00:14:03,370
Bye, Senior!

157
00:14:03,370 --> 00:14:05,950
Let go of my hand.

158
00:14:06,969 --> 00:14:08,950
Wait for me!

159
00:14:08,950 --> 00:14:12,269
Can you be more sympathetic? I'm a patient after all.

160
00:14:12,269 --> 00:14:14,768
I shouldn't have gifted you that book.

161
00:14:14,769 --> 00:14:17,609
Had I known it was so dangerous, I wouldn't have let you study veterinary medicine.

162
00:14:17,609 --> 00:14:22,300
It's more dangerous than treating humans. What if you get rabies?

163
00:14:22,300 --> 00:14:25,130
If I get rabies, I'll bite you first.

164
00:14:26,009 --> 00:14:30,108
It's too late to regret it! I've made up my mind... I'll take care of animals, forever.

165
00:14:31,050 --> 00:14:34,930
Fine, you never listen to me after all. Forget it!

166
00:14:35,730 --> 00:14:39,330
Thanks for the book.

167
00:14:39,330 --> 00:14:41,490
As long as you like it.

168
00:14:45,290 --> 00:14:47,610
- You're back!
- You're back!

169
00:14:47,610 --> 00:14:49,929
Aren't you supposed to get off work at five?

170
00:14:53,730 --> 00:14:57,930
Oh, yeah, Xu Fang left without finishing practice today.

171
00:14:57,930 --> 00:15:00,169
He came to see me.

172
00:15:00,169 --> 00:15:04,740
I thought these things are all from Senior Ye.

173
00:15:04,740 --> 00:15:07,990
What a disappointment!

174
00:15:07,990 --> 00:15:09,929
I never thought it's Xu Fang.

175
00:15:12,170 --> 00:15:15,008
You're not happy with Xu Fang giving them to you?

176
00:15:15,009 --> 00:15:17,209
That's not what I meant.

177
00:15:17,209 --> 00:15:20,430
Just that, I was reading the book

178
00:15:20,430 --> 00:15:24,430
with Senior Ye on my mind and I did the same while drinking water.

179
00:15:24,430 --> 00:15:27,009
I even sent him a picture.

180
00:15:27,009 --> 00:15:30,050
And I was wrong.

181
00:15:30,050 --> 00:15:32,970
Besides, I've been so mean to Xu Fang recently.

182
00:15:32,970 --> 00:15:37,809
- It feels as if I've done wrong and owe him something.
- I think it should be fine.

183
00:15:37,809 --> 00:15:42,909
You can just get Xu Fang something for his birthday.

184
00:15:43,510 --> 00:15:45,790
That's doable!

185
00:15:52,416 --> 00:15:55,316
[All Things Bright and Beautiful]

186
00:16:00,930 --> 00:16:04,229
Look at your test paper! You didn't do this big question at the end.

187
00:16:04,229 --> 00:16:07,568
I've explained every question for so many times in class.

188
00:16:07,569 --> 00:16:10,729
I've always said that these were all basics.

189
00:16:10,730 --> 00:16:13,250
And you really don't know how to answer them?

190
00:16:14,569 --> 00:16:18,709
When my daughter was at Grade Three, she only slept for four hours every night.

191
00:16:18,709 --> 00:16:23,969
When I went to bed, the light in her room was still on, and she woke up way before me.

192
00:16:23,969 --> 00:16:26,390
You're sure she was studying?

193
00:16:26,390 --> 00:16:28,869
What else could she do?

194
00:16:28,869 --> 00:16:33,030
Maybe she's doing what she likes when you're not looking.

195
00:16:33,030 --> 00:16:35,709
She likes studying.

196
00:16:35,709 --> 00:16:37,730
Then, you should...

197
00:16:38,529 --> 00:16:41,029
Does Teacher He know her daughter flunked a grade?

198
00:16:41,029 --> 00:16:45,389
Is your mother Teacher He who teaches Mathematics at Luo City High School?

199
00:16:46,009 --> 00:16:47,610
What do you want?

200
00:16:48,889 --> 00:16:53,089
You're right! I should learn from her.

201
00:16:54,030 --> 00:16:56,630
Okay! Go back to your class.

202
00:16:56,630 --> 00:16:59,049
Thank you, teacher. Goodbye.

203
00:16:59,049 --> 00:17:01,568
- Walk properly!
- I'm used to it.

204
00:17:01,568 --> 00:17:04,401
[Building De]

205
00:17:04,401 --> 00:17:09,544
[Passion as the fuel of exam, hard work earns success.]

206
00:17:14,449 --> 00:17:17,650
Why does this question look so familiar?

207
00:17:23,329 --> 00:17:26,730
I was wondering why this question looks so familiar?

208
00:17:29,410 --> 00:17:34,170
This question, too! You're really something, Big Li.

209
00:17:35,589 --> 00:17:37,709
- Let me use it.
- That's mine!

210
00:17:37,709 --> 00:17:39,769
- Give it back to me!
- Just for a while!

211
00:17:39,769 --> 00:17:41,450
Give it back to me!

212
00:17:42,590 --> 00:17:46,669
What a good secret scripture! They're all original questions.

213
00:17:46,669 --> 00:17:48,869
It seems very useful, let me have a look at it first! Let me see.

214
00:17:48,869 --> 00:17:52,000
Give it back! Keep your voice down.

215
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:54,589
Once I finish this, I'll lend you the book.

216
00:17:54,589 --> 00:17:56,569
I'll take your word for it.

217
00:18:03,529 --> 00:18:05,410
Eat more fish!

218
00:18:10,370 --> 00:18:12,270
Let me take a look!

219
00:18:12,270 --> 00:18:14,968
- I'm fine.
- A dog bit you?

220
00:18:14,968 --> 00:18:17,450
I've got vaccinated.

221
00:18:17,450 --> 00:18:20,009
That's why I didn't agree for you to study medicine when you were young.

222
00:18:20,010 --> 00:18:23,228
I know everything about this field, it's a very tough job.

223
00:18:23,228 --> 00:18:27,708
When I realized you're an animal lover, I decided to tell you about veterinary medicine.

224
00:18:27,708 --> 00:18:32,300
When you begged for studying it, I was secretly happy about your decision for a while.

225
00:18:32,350 --> 00:18:34,630
It seems that it's worse to be a vet.

226
00:18:34,630 --> 00:18:37,550
It's a dirty and tiring job, and you get bitten by animals.

227
00:18:37,550 --> 00:18:40,589
I really regret telling you about this.

228
00:18:43,610 --> 00:18:45,490
Is it painful?

229
00:18:47,530 --> 00:18:49,630
My heart feels painful.

230
00:18:49,630 --> 00:18:53,850
Becoming a great doctor like you has always been my ambition.

231
00:18:54,850 --> 00:18:59,309
That's why I came here, the city where you live, to study.

232
00:18:59,309 --> 00:19:03,750
I've now fulfilled part of my life ambition.

233
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:05,789
I feel very content.

234
00:19:06,909 --> 00:19:10,609
Mom, I want to be

235
00:19:10,609 --> 00:19:13,630
as excellent as you.

236
00:19:18,490 --> 00:19:21,269
Chinese New Year is in a month.

237
00:19:21,269 --> 00:19:26,249
Can our whole family celebrate it at Rong City?

238
00:19:27,169 --> 00:19:31,009
We'll ask dad and Geng-geng to come here.

239
00:19:31,009 --> 00:19:33,229
We'll have a family reunion.

240
00:19:36,010 --> 00:19:39,529
It's been years since we last celebrated it together.

241
00:19:39,529 --> 00:19:41,830
Can we?

242
00:19:46,570 --> 00:19:48,770
Is that a yes?

243
00:19:48,770 --> 00:19:51,390
But bear this in mind.

244
00:19:51,390 --> 00:19:54,910
You know there will be many emergencies during Chinese New Year.

245
00:19:54,910 --> 00:19:57,249
I won't have many days off.

246
00:19:57,250 --> 00:20:02,089
I do know that. No problem! You just need to spend a day with us.

247
00:20:06,250 --> 00:20:09,608
Be careful next time! Can you take it easy?

248
00:20:09,608 --> 00:20:11,870
I got it, mom.

249
00:20:13,049 --> 00:20:16,628
- Can you eat fish? You just had an injection after all.
- I can eat it.

250
00:20:17,310 --> 00:20:20,110
Don't eat too much spicy food! Eat more meat.

251
00:20:23,130 --> 00:20:27,269
Hello, Changge! I just met Chi-chi.

252
00:20:27,269 --> 00:20:32,009
She said she wanted you and Geng-geng to celebrate Chinese New Year at Rong City.

253
00:20:32,009 --> 00:20:33,930
And you said yes?

254
00:20:34,809 --> 00:20:36,509
Yes.

255
00:20:37,929 --> 00:20:39,929
Great!

256
00:20:40,730 --> 00:20:43,270
I don't want to keep them in the dark anymore.

257
00:20:43,270 --> 00:20:48,429
I can't imagine the moment when they find out we've been lying to them,

258
00:20:48,429 --> 00:20:50,970
how can I explain myself?

259
00:20:50,970 --> 00:20:53,509
We've talked about this.

260
00:20:53,509 --> 00:20:58,209
They were young, and we had a lot of concerns.

261
00:20:58,209 --> 00:21:03,150
But they've grown up and become independent.

262
00:21:03,890 --> 00:21:08,490
Maybe it's time to tell them the truth.

263
00:21:19,250 --> 00:21:20,568
This is the weather station of Rong City.

264
00:21:20,569 --> 00:21:22,409
Today is twelve of November, 2015.

265
00:21:22,410 --> 00:21:24,389
We're declaring a Code Blue warning for a coming cold wave.

266
00:21:24,490 --> 00:21:26,048
It is expected to be a cold wave on the thirteenth and fourteenth.

267
00:21:26,049 --> 00:21:28,769
on the thirteenth and fourteenth day.

268
00:21:28,770 --> 00:21:32,370
At the night of the thirteenth, the lowest temperature would be -5 Celsius.

269
00:21:32,370 --> 00:21:35,189
Please take care!

270
00:21:38,329 --> 00:21:39,829
- I'm here!
- Why are you here?

271
00:21:39,829 --> 00:21:41,729
You said you'd come after you recovered.

272
00:21:41,730 --> 00:21:43,629
I was worried, so I came to check on them.

273
00:21:43,629 --> 00:21:45,608
See, I'm good now! The wound has healed.

274
00:21:45,608 --> 00:21:47,890
You're really an animal lover.

275
00:21:47,890 --> 00:21:50,588
- This is your field.
- Thank you.

276
00:21:50,588 --> 00:21:52,228
How were they doing these two days?

277
00:21:52,228 --> 00:21:54,329
Not so good.

278
00:21:54,329 --> 00:21:55,988
They're barking all the time.

279
00:21:55,988 --> 00:21:59,688
Especially at nights. When I leave, the light is off, the door is locked,

280
00:21:59,688 --> 00:22:03,160
they would start barking as if the world had abandoned them.

281
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:05,709
They behave when you're around; look! they've stopped barking.

282
00:22:05,709 --> 00:22:10,400
And they're embarrassed to see you here as though they've done something wrong.

283
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:13,348
- They're like kids.
- I know, right?

284
00:22:13,348 --> 00:22:16,188
They're kids with fur and IQ of a three- or four-year-old.

285
00:22:16,188 --> 00:22:19,208
They were separated from their mothers when they were small.

286
00:22:19,209 --> 00:22:24,249
They're afraid of getting separated and their fears get worse at night.

287
00:22:25,610 --> 00:22:28,650
Then, why did their owner leave them here?

288
00:22:28,650 --> 00:22:31,010
And they've been staying here for long.

289
00:22:31,530 --> 00:22:33,389
I think their owner's a writer.

290
00:22:33,389 --> 00:22:35,550
She lives alone and she's gone somewhere for inspiration.

291
00:22:35,550 --> 00:22:38,269
They're sent here because no one could take care of them.

292
00:22:38,269 --> 00:22:41,449
She called yesterday and said they'd stay here for two more weeks.

293
00:22:43,289 --> 00:22:46,369
Your mother's a writer.

294
00:22:46,370 --> 00:22:49,170
And my mother's a doctor.

295
00:22:49,170 --> 00:22:50,729
They're busy working.

296
00:22:50,730 --> 00:22:54,830
Be good and wait for your mother to pick you up, okay?

297
00:23:21,890 --> 00:23:26,088
- What?
- Don't litter here! Or else, I'll punch you!

298
00:23:27,730 --> 00:23:29,870
You're so uncultured.

299
00:23:33,250 --> 00:23:34,950
Feeling tired?

300
00:23:37,389 --> 00:23:39,310
Thanks.

301
00:23:44,250 --> 00:23:46,109
Your milk tea is here!

302
00:23:46,109 --> 00:23:47,849
Milk tea? There's milk tea.

303
00:23:47,849 --> 00:23:49,810
- Help yourselves!
- Come one, come all!

304
00:23:49,810 --> 00:23:52,649
Brother Fu, why are you being so nice?

305
00:23:52,649 --> 00:23:54,409
What?

306
00:23:54,410 --> 00:23:57,189
On my way back here, I bumped into Lin Xichi.

307
00:23:57,189 --> 00:24:01,469
I wanted to buy her milk tea but she asked me to buy it for you all.

308
00:24:01,469 --> 00:24:05,080
And I listened to her. Here, help yourself!

309
00:24:05,080 --> 00:24:09,130
- You're not pursuing her anymore?
- We're brothers now.

310
00:24:09,130 --> 00:24:11,068
Good brothers!

311
00:24:12,670 --> 00:24:17,070
But we seldom see each other now.

312
00:24:17,070 --> 00:24:19,209
And I feel quite down.

313
00:24:19,209 --> 00:24:21,530
Then, why didn't you ask her to come here?

314
00:24:21,530 --> 00:24:24,130
I did! But she just got off work.

315
00:24:24,130 --> 00:24:26,570
She was tired, so she went back to the dorm.

316
00:24:33,390 --> 00:24:37,690
You... reserved a cup for me.

317
00:24:37,690 --> 00:24:39,750
You heard that?

318
00:24:40,530 --> 00:24:41,769
Come here.

319
00:24:41,770 --> 00:24:43,328
Let me have a bite!

320
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:46,300
- Brother Fu, me too!
- Me too!

321
00:24:46,300 --> 00:24:49,529
You saw that, didn't you? Come here!

322
00:24:49,529 --> 00:24:53,210
You get it now? I've given you all my advice.

323
00:24:53,210 --> 00:24:55,489
Can you think of a way yourself?

324
00:24:55,489 --> 00:24:59,609
You're going to let her mingle with Ye Shaowen all the time? You'll lose her, eventually.

325
00:24:59,609 --> 00:25:03,509
She has the right to make her choice and she's doing things related to her major.

326
00:25:03,509 --> 00:25:06,529
I shouldn't blame her for working hard towards her profession.

327
00:25:06,530 --> 00:25:09,309
No.

328
00:25:09,309 --> 00:25:12,609
If you like her, you should go see her more often.

329
00:25:12,609 --> 00:25:14,689
Take the initiative.

330
00:25:16,569 --> 00:25:19,949
She spends most of her time with Ye Shaowen.

331
00:25:19,949 --> 00:25:22,889
Brother, you know how slow she is.

332
00:25:22,889 --> 00:25:25,490
If she gives in and get together with Ye Shaowen, what will you do?

333
00:25:25,490 --> 00:25:30,169
Are you going to cry? I don't think there would be any tears left for you to cry.

334
00:25:31,610 --> 00:25:33,730
A forcefully picked melon isn't sweet!
(TN: I can't force her.)

335
00:25:35,869 --> 00:25:39,488
Did you even try to pick it? You're not confident with yourself?

336
00:25:39,488 --> 00:25:43,600
We've been friends for so long, didn't you learn something useful from me?

337
00:25:48,670 --> 00:25:52,170
- Yue-yue.
- Why are you here again?

338
00:25:52,910 --> 00:25:56,088
What day is today? Fu Kuankuan bought us milk tea and you bought us snacks.

339
00:25:56,088 --> 00:25:57,590
Thanks.

340
00:25:59,709 --> 00:26:02,049
I'm going there, carry on with your work!

341
00:26:10,890 --> 00:26:12,690
Xu Fang.

342
00:26:17,569 --> 00:26:19,210
Have some snacks!

343
00:26:19,210 --> 00:26:23,229
It's cold these days, you should eat more to replenish your energy.

344
00:26:26,270 --> 00:26:29,350
- Thank you.
- Don't mention it!

345
00:26:29,350 --> 00:26:31,690
- I...
- I...

346
00:26:31,690 --> 00:26:33,989
You go ahead.

347
00:26:34,670 --> 00:26:36,969
I have a question.

348
00:26:37,750 --> 00:26:40,669
Has Lin Xichi recovered from her injury?

349
00:26:41,809 --> 00:26:46,389
She... She didn't say much about it.

350
00:26:46,389 --> 00:26:49,090
I think there're two more injections.

351
00:26:50,329 --> 00:26:53,030
I also need to ask you for a favor.

352
00:26:53,030 --> 00:26:57,470
I think she has a serious injury and you're her roommate after all.

353
00:26:57,470 --> 00:27:03,110
If possible, can you take care of her more often and keep her arm dry?

354
00:27:07,769 --> 00:27:09,669
Is that okay?

355
00:27:10,449 --> 00:27:12,708
Sure, don't worry.

356
00:27:12,708 --> 00:27:14,389
I got it.

357
00:27:14,389 --> 00:27:17,600
Thank you! I'll carry on with practice.

358
00:27:59,910 --> 00:28:02,069
Why are you here?

359
00:28:02,130 --> 00:28:05,828
It's late! It's not safe for you to walk back to the dorm alone.

360
00:28:05,828 --> 00:28:07,469
I'll walk you back.

361
00:28:07,469 --> 00:28:10,149
But what's this posture for?

362
00:28:12,570 --> 00:28:15,750
Isn't this what they do in dramas?

363
00:28:27,790 --> 00:28:31,188
What a good day! There're so many stars.

364
00:28:32,069 --> 00:28:33,669
I know, right?

365
00:28:43,869 --> 00:28:45,569
What's this?

366
00:28:45,569 --> 00:28:47,310
It's for you.

367
00:28:48,510 --> 00:28:53,208
Today's not my birthday or some special occasion, why are you giving me a present?

368
00:28:53,208 --> 00:28:55,530
I wish that we...

369
00:28:56,670 --> 00:28:58,890
can be friends forever.

370
00:29:00,790 --> 00:29:03,470
I can't accept it for no reason; I don't want it.

371
00:29:07,290 --> 00:29:10,769
You know very well what's on my mind.

372
00:29:10,769 --> 00:29:14,869
I don't know what's on your mind.

373
00:29:14,869 --> 00:29:19,789
Then, can I know what's on your mind?

374
00:29:26,470 --> 00:29:29,449
Have you seen the movie yet?

375
00:29:29,449 --> 00:29:31,470
What's the title?

376
00:29:31,470 --> 00:29:33,610
Tangled.

377
00:29:35,490 --> 00:29:38,070
- I'm going to see it now.
- You're not sending me back?

378
00:29:38,070 --> 00:29:40,090
Oh, yeah,

379
00:29:41,269 --> 00:29:43,009
here's your present.

380
00:29:43,009 --> 00:29:45,949
I'm talking about sending me back to my dorm.

381
00:29:53,969 --> 00:29:57,530
Brother, we've seen it three times.

382
00:29:57,530 --> 00:29:59,630
Let's do something else!

383
00:29:59,630 --> 00:30:03,588
Not until we get what it's about! Analyze it for me.

384
00:30:03,588 --> 00:30:06,328
I don't find it meaningful at all.

385
00:30:06,329 --> 00:30:08,509
Isn't it for kids below twelve?

386
00:30:08,509 --> 00:30:12,410
- Am I not intelligent enough?
- Then, let's watch it one more time.

387
00:30:13,610 --> 00:30:16,770
I'm not this attentive even when I'm playing games.

388
00:30:16,770 --> 00:30:18,510
Should we play some game first?

389
00:30:18,510 --> 00:30:22,810
Get lost! We're not playing a game until we get what it's about!

390
00:30:30,449 --> 00:30:34,090
What are you all doing? Three men watching a movie, that's disgusting!

391
00:30:34,090 --> 00:30:36,589
Captain Fang, you're finally back.

392
00:30:36,589 --> 00:30:38,309
Jiang Zhengxu confessed to Nie Yue.

393
00:30:38,309 --> 00:30:41,468
She asked him to solve a difficult puzzle by watching this Barbie animation.

394
00:30:41,468 --> 00:30:45,489
We've seen it four times and we still don't get what this girl's trying to say.

395
00:30:45,489 --> 00:30:47,870
I'm so sick of watching it.

396
00:30:48,490 --> 00:30:50,469
Tangled?

397
00:30:50,469 --> 00:30:52,310
You've seen it?

398
00:30:53,289 --> 00:30:57,189
Lin Xichi used to force me to watch Disney animated movies with her when we were young.

399
00:30:59,630 --> 00:31:01,408
I told you! Xu Fang's our savior.

400
00:31:01,408 --> 00:31:03,370
Analyze it for me!

401
00:31:04,569 --> 00:31:09,269
Then, was Nie Yue in a relationship?

402
00:31:09,820 --> 00:31:11,770
No.

403
00:31:11,770 --> 00:31:13,389
Weren't you in the same high school as her?

404
00:31:13,389 --> 00:31:17,050
- Did anyone pursue her?
- Of course, not!

405
00:31:17,050 --> 00:31:22,049
She had this serious look and always pulled a long face.

406
00:31:23,670 --> 00:31:26,310
Go to bed now, I don't need you anymore.

407
00:31:27,329 --> 00:31:30,030
That makes sense!

408
00:31:30,030 --> 00:31:33,669
Look, Nie Yue is excellent and she is a class president.

409
00:31:33,669 --> 00:31:37,889
She the kind of person where teachers see her as a good student.

410
00:31:37,889 --> 00:31:41,348
Parents see her as a good kid, am I right?

411
00:31:41,348 --> 00:31:45,149
So, she asked you to watch this movie and wanted to tell you that

412
00:31:45,149 --> 00:31:49,809
she's torn because two people are fighting one another in her head.

413
00:31:50,750 --> 00:31:52,890
How did you find that out?

414
00:31:52,890 --> 00:31:54,769
Look at this movie!

415
00:31:54,769 --> 00:31:58,588
Rapunzel has been living in this small cabin up in a high tower.

416
00:31:58,588 --> 00:32:00,309
Why doesn't she come down?

417
00:32:00,309 --> 00:32:03,889
First, she's trying to maintain her image as a good kid

418
00:32:03,890 --> 00:32:05,549
and a good student.

419
00:32:05,549 --> 00:32:09,569
Second, she's curious about the prince down at the bottom of the tower.

420
00:32:10,589 --> 00:32:14,430
She's considering to let down her long hair for the prince.

421
00:32:14,430 --> 00:32:18,730
I think this is the psychological state Nie Yue's going through.

422
00:32:21,490 --> 00:32:23,529
That's enough! Stop watching.

423
00:32:23,530 --> 00:32:26,930
Trust me! Just chase after her, it's definitely correct.

424
00:32:50,150 --> 00:32:53,469
L1 is always perpendicular to L2.

425
00:32:53,469 --> 00:32:57,677
Find the chord length of the intersection between the straight line and conic curve.

426
00:33:00,550 --> 00:33:04,869
Lin Xigeng, what are you looking at?

427
00:33:04,869 --> 00:33:08,710
Me? I was listening to the question.

428
00:33:09,449 --> 00:33:11,228
That's very unusual.

429
00:33:11,228 --> 00:33:14,210
You're actually paying attention to my lesson?

430
00:33:15,890 --> 00:33:17,390
Here.

431
00:33:17,390 --> 00:33:20,770
Come and solve this question.

432
00:33:22,100 --> 00:33:24,069
He's dead meat!

433
00:33:24,069 --> 00:33:26,957
What a boot-licker!

434
00:33:35,816 --> 00:33:37,976
[Passion as the fuel of exam, hard work earns success.]

435
00:34:03,010 --> 00:34:05,310
I came across this question before.

436
00:34:05,929 --> 00:34:10,049
It looks like as long as you're willing to work hard, it's never too late.

437
00:34:22,510 --> 00:34:24,930
Can you lend me your secret scripture?

438
00:34:24,930 --> 00:34:27,469
- Me, too!
- Sure!

439
00:34:28,849 --> 00:34:31,850
Coach, when will we start our winter break?

440
00:34:31,850 --> 00:34:36,509
I've forgotten to tell you, our school has arranged a winter training for us.

441
00:34:36,509 --> 00:34:39,449
- Winter training?
- It'll be about two weeks.

442
00:34:39,449 --> 00:34:41,888
We'll go to the shooting and archery center in the neighboring province.

443
00:34:41,888 --> 00:34:45,130
Learn from others and improve ourselves.

444
00:34:45,130 --> 00:34:47,328
You'll go home for the New Year after the winter training.

445
00:34:47,328 --> 00:34:49,649
Two weeks, Coach!

446
00:34:49,649 --> 00:34:51,609
It's not a long holiday to begin with.

447
00:34:51,610 --> 00:34:55,270
We will be home for less than ten days now.

448
00:34:55,270 --> 00:34:57,290
Yu Tong, pull yourself together!

449
00:34:57,290 --> 00:34:59,149
Can you be more manly?

450
00:34:59,149 --> 00:35:01,089
Practice in ten minutes!

451
00:35:01,089 --> 00:35:02,808
Let's start practice.

452
00:35:02,809 --> 00:35:05,108
- Let's go for practice.
- Okay.

453
00:35:06,870 --> 00:35:09,889
Captain, what do we do?

454
00:35:09,889 --> 00:35:12,870
I was thinking about going home for a good rest.

455
00:35:12,870 --> 00:35:14,490
I think it's good.

456
00:35:14,490 --> 00:35:16,529
It's a rare opportunity.

457
00:35:18,249 --> 00:35:20,249
I'll go practice now.

458
00:35:23,410 --> 00:35:25,010
What's so good about it?

459
00:35:25,010 --> 00:35:26,749
Have you gone crazy?

460
00:35:26,749 --> 00:35:29,069
You can go home and see Lin Xichi.

461
00:35:29,069 --> 00:35:31,249
What for?

462
00:35:37,049 --> 00:35:39,869
Let me pet you, let me pet you!

463
00:35:40,830 --> 00:35:43,069
Lin Xichi, take a break!

464
00:35:43,069 --> 00:35:44,970
I'm fine.

465
00:35:44,970 --> 00:35:49,789
It's been a month, why hasn't their owner come to get them?

466
00:35:49,789 --> 00:35:51,728
Their mother called today.

467
00:35:51,729 --> 00:35:53,288
She said she can't get home for New Year.

468
00:35:53,289 --> 00:35:56,849
It seems that they're going to celebrate it here.

469
00:35:56,849 --> 00:35:59,049
That's so pitiful!

470
00:35:59,049 --> 00:36:00,969
Just like when I was small.

471
00:36:00,970 --> 00:36:05,949
My brother and I were waiting for our mother to come home every day.

472
00:36:05,949 --> 00:36:07,609
But this year is different.

473
00:36:07,610 --> 00:36:11,348
We'll celebrate it with our mother. Are you happy?

474
00:36:11,348 --> 00:36:15,109
But I'll come and see you two.

475
00:36:15,109 --> 00:36:17,350
You're going to miss me, aren't you?

476
00:36:26,030 --> 00:36:29,009
Geng-geng, you're doing homework?

477
00:36:30,489 --> 00:36:32,148
I have something to tell you.

478
00:36:32,148 --> 00:36:37,029
New Year's in a few days and we're going to Rong City.

479
00:36:37,029 --> 00:36:38,649
What for?

480
00:36:38,649 --> 00:36:41,528
It'll be crowded everywhere, why don't we just stay at home?

481
00:36:41,529 --> 00:36:44,829
- I'm not going.
- You have to!

482
00:36:44,829 --> 00:36:48,248
We're going to celebrate it with your mother and sister.

483
00:36:48,249 --> 00:36:51,030
Wait! What's going on here?

484
00:36:51,030 --> 00:36:53,728
- Did you suggest that, dad?
- No.

485
00:36:53,728 --> 00:36:58,369
- My mom?
- Cut your crap and just come.

486
00:36:58,369 --> 00:37:00,749
Can't they just come back here?

487
00:37:00,749 --> 00:37:05,008
We never celebrated New Year in another city all these years; and, it's so cold out there.

488
00:37:05,008 --> 00:37:09,068
You're not coming? Then, you'll stay here alone.

489
00:37:22,569 --> 00:37:24,568
Are you celebrating New Year at Luo City?

490
00:37:24,569 --> 00:37:27,969
My dad wants to celebrate it at Rong City.

491
00:37:27,969 --> 00:37:30,280
[He Liyang]

492
00:37:31,289 --> 00:37:34,429
I'm thinking of seeing you during the winter break.

493
00:37:34,429 --> 00:37:38,128
Did you know, the exercise book you gave me is like a secret scripture?

494
00:37:38,128 --> 00:37:40,789
All my classmates asked me to lend them.

495
00:37:41,930 --> 00:37:46,429
- You've done them all?
- Yes, I've done a quarter of them.

496
00:37:47,130 --> 00:37:48,889
Let's do this instead!

497
00:37:48,889 --> 00:37:51,609
Finish them all and I'll see you.

498
00:37:51,610 --> 00:37:53,940
I'll give you one for another subject.

499
00:37:54,630 --> 00:37:58,349
Then, I need to work hard and finish six books before the exam.

500
00:37:58,349 --> 00:38:00,230
I need to master all subjects.

501
00:38:00,849 --> 00:38:02,909
That's a bit late!

502
00:38:02,909 --> 00:38:05,929
Do it in this winter break, or I won't see you.

503
00:38:06,650 --> 00:38:08,450
